.jumbotron
  h1 Laser Sharks

  p Welcome to Laser Sharks. This Rails app was (recently) developed by Lighthouse Labs for students to use on a constant basis to interact with the course curriculum.

  - if current_user
    = link_to day_path('today'), class: 'btn btn-hg btn-success'
      span Get to Work! &raquo;

  - else
    p In order to use Laser Sharks, you must first authenticate via Github...

    = link_to new_session_path, class: 'btn btn-hg btn-primary'
      span Let's Get Started &raquo;
